
To Install Minikube
---------------------

curl -LO https://storage.googleapis.com/minikube/releases/latest/minikube-linux-amd64
sudo install minikube-linux-amd64 /usr/local/bin/minikube

minikube version

minikube start
minikube addons enable ingress
minikube ip
sudo vi /etc/hosts
vim /etc/hosts

add entry againt IP from minikube ip to frontend and backend as frontend.minikube.local and backend.minikube.local

to Install Kubectl
-------------------

chmod +x kubectl
sudo mv kubectl /usr/local/bin/
kubectl version


minikube status


to Install Helm
----------------

curl -LO https://get.helm.sh/helm-v3.1.1-linux-amd64.tar.gz

> tar -xzvf helm-v3.1.1-linux-amd64.tar.gz 
linux-amd64/
linux-amd64/README.md
linux-amd64/LICENSE
linux-amd64/helm

> lenovo@ubuntu:~$ sudo mv linux-amd64/helm /usr/local/bin/helm

> helm version --short
> kubectl version --short
> kubectl config view


Helm Commands:
------------------------

> helm repo update
> helm install demo-mysql stable/mysql
> helm repo add stable https://kubernetes-charts.storage.googleapis.com/
> kubectl get all  | grep mysql
